<span id="freeTextContainer18323733877052021885">ARC from Netgalley. The synopsis for this probably doesn&apos;t do it justice or give quite the right vibe for this book. Jesse is a divorced dad who suddenly finds his life spiralling. The author describes poignantly the descent of his mother into early dementia. Then we have his son&apos;s relationship with a pastors daughter - but the pastor is far from godly. Jesse has a bad track record with the women in his life too. Add in some financial and business challenges and Jesse finds life taking him in so</span>
  <span id="freeText18323733877052021885" style="display:none">ARC from Netgalley. The synopsis for this probably doesn't do it justice or give quite the right vibe for this book. Jesse is a divorced dad who suddenly finds his life spiralling. The author describes poignantly the descent of his mother into early dementia. Then we have his son's relationship with a pastors daughter - but the pastor is far from godly. Jesse has a bad track record with the women in his life too. Add in some financial and business challenges and Jesse finds life taking him in some surprising but ultimately beneficial directions.</span>
