<span id="freeTextContainer14298746896456184213">I received an ARC from NetGalley. I really wanted to love this book. I liked it but it just felt odd. I couldn&apos;t really connect with any of the characters. The premise was one I can totally understand since I am in sales and have survived the recession. It probably would be a great premise for a movie though.</span>
  <span id="freeText14298746896456184213" style="display:none">I received an ARC from NetGalley. I really wanted to love this book. I liked it but it just felt odd. I couldn't really connect with any of the characters. The premise was one I can totally understand since I am in sales and have survived the recession. It probably would be a great premise for a movie though.</span>
